OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly dry, but cloudy start,
OL,6,Fbefore outbreaks of rain, locally
OL,7,Fheavy, spread eastwards across all
OL,8,Fparts during the morning. Winds light
OL,9,Finitially but becoming breezy at times
OL,10,Fduring the afternoon. Feeling rather
OL,11,Fhumid through the afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain will mostly clear
OL,14,Feastwards overnight although remaining
OL,15,Flargely cloudy. A few isolated showers
OL,16,Fremain possible however. Some clearer
OL,17,Fspells may develop towards dawn.
OL,18,FBreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
