OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FVariable cloud and sunny
OL,6,Fspells expected for much of the day,
OL,7,Fmany areas remaining dry but a few
OL,8,Flight outbreaks of rain are possible
OL,9,Fat times. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,12,FGenerally dry through this period with
OL,13,Fpatchy cloud and sunny spells. Breezy
OL,14,Fon Saturday but winds falling light
OL,15,Ffor Sunday and Monday. Feeling warm,
OL,16,Fespecially in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
